4.title: Balinese Curry and a Colourful Salad
4.plot: Jamie bakes colourful bread to go with spinach, cheese and eggs, and makes a spicy Balinese curry with shiitake mushrooms for dinner

5.title: Crumble, Ravioli and Tomato Sauce
5.plot: Jamie visits Sardinia and South Korea and cooks a toasted fruit crumble, squash and ricotta ravioli, and a vegetable tomato sauce

imdb.plot outline: Jamie's Super Food is an exciting new series where you can learn how to eat your way to a healthier life. Each week Jamie cooks up a day's worth of delicious meals - perfectly balanced plates of mouthwatering food that have all the good nutrition you need in a day.
